{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247635, "create_time": 1655960834, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "人前:量中华之物力，结与国之欢心\n人后:美国是全球第一抗疫失败国，第一恐怖主义国，第一政治甩锅国", "timestamp": 1655960834}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247643, "create_time": 1655960989, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 不太熟悉近代史的人们通常认为，“宁赠友邦，不予家奴”是慈禧太后的最高指示，其实不然。笔者俭学，这“八字方针”不载于史籍，近似的说法见于梁启超的《戊戌政变记》：“故刚毅常语人云：‘我家之产业，宁可以赠之于朋友，而必不畀诸家奴。’朋友谓於俄国，家奴谓汉人也。”（《戊戌政变记》卷四，页14）梁文表述明确，说者乃刚毅而非慈禧，只不过“朋友”隐含了“友邦”（俄国），“家奴”特指了“汉人”，总体意思是不差的。", "timestamp": 1655960989}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247646, "create_time": 1655961015, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re : 井😭 懂得真多哇", "timestamp": 1655961015}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247648, "create_time": 1655961115, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: #卡大佐", "timestamp": 1655961115}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247653, "create_time": 1655961155, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "邹容在“量中华之物力，结友邦之欢心”的后文，激愤地写道：“中国者，中国人之中国也。割我同胞之土地，抢我同胞之财产，以买其一家一姓五百万家奴（这里的“家奴”是指满清统治阶层）一日之安逸，此割台湾、胶州之本心，所以感发五中矣！”", "timestamp": 1655961155}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247654, "create_time": 1655961171, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Carol: 🤗🤗🤗", "timestamp": 1655961171}], "create_time": 1655960453, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1655961171, "likenum": 3, "n_attentions": 3, "n_comments": 6, "pid": 71053, "poll": null, "reply": 6, "text": "“量中华之物力 结与国之欢心”\n现在懂了为什么慈禧会说这句话了，自己统治才是最重要的\n宁予友邦，不予家奴", "timestamp": 1655960453}}